title: Vespa PX 150  '79
description: To montelo einai vespa pe 150,Egine oliki anakatsaskeyi to 2018 kalokairi,i anakataskeyi stoihise 3600€ sinolika,exei ola ta timologia apo tin agora olwn twn antalaktikwn ta opia einai gnisia axias 1800€ kai agorastikan apo to scootershop, oliki anakataskeyi sto moter me 3800 hiliometra, se apsogi katastasi filasete se klisto garaz! - Less -
